    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the dazzling world of Super Star Battle! Place stars in a grid, one in each row, column, and area. But watch out, they are not allowed to touch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225450/extras/8b5cb12c9eb9c9abc7a4af0c2587e467.poster.avif?t=1756853907\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225450/extras/8b5cb12c9eb9c9abc7a4af0c2587e467.webm?t=1756853907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225450/extras/8b5cb12c9eb9c9abc7a4af0c2587e467.mp4?t=1756853907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through numerous levels, of increasing difficulty. Spend your points on unlocking new Levels, of bigger sizes and more stars to place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play <strong>5x5</strong> Grid with <strong>5</strong> Stars</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play <strong>7x7</strong> Grid with <strong>7</strong> Stars</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play <strong>9x9</strong> Grid with <strong>18</strong> Stars</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play <strong>13x13</strong> Grid with <strong>39</strong> Stars</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>and more ...</strong></p>",
